headline.main: Cuba’s Raul Castro Blasts Trump’s Mexican Wall and Trade Policy
headline.print_headline: Cuba’s Raul Castro Blasts Trump’s Mexican Wall and Trade Policy

lead_paragraph: Our Lady of Peace, shuttered since 2015, was opened to the local parish of the Coptic Orthodox Church after a lease was granted at the direction of Cardinal Timothy M. Dolan.
